      "content": "that makes sense, the price hike thing is definitely a worry. but i also hear people arguing that higher wages actually help the local economy because workers spend more. i'm trying to figure out if that's actually a real thing for a small shop like mine or if it's just a theoretical idea that doesn't work in practice in small towns.",
