      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "From a purely business standpoint, the foundation rests on your ability to manage costs while maintaining competitive pricing and demand. While the social argument is compelling, the economic impact is highly dependent on your specific local market elasticity—how sensitive your customers are to price changes. Ultimately, the most solid foundation is a proactive business plan that anticipates cost increases while maximizing efficiency.",
